A D O P T I O N S U P P L E M E N T
F.E.R.C. No. 3.0.0 Cancels Supplement No. 1 to F.E.R.C. No. 1
RAZORBACK L.L.C. dba DIAMONDBACK PIPELINE L.L.C.
Local Tariff Applying on Petroleum Products From Brownsville, Cameron County, Texas, to the United States/Mexico International Boundary (near Brownsville in Cameron County, Texas)
Effective on December 31, 2007, this tariff publication became the tariff of Razorback L.L.C. dba Diamondback Pipeline L.L.C as per its adoption notice FERC No. 1.
Issued in Compliance with 18 CFR 341.6 (c)
[N] Filed in compliance with Order No. 714 - Electronic Tariff Filings, issued on September 19, 2008, for the establishment of Baseline Tariff. The provisions published herein will, if effective, not result in an effect on the quality of the human environment.
ISSUED: March 21, 2011 EFFECTIVE: April 21, 2011
